(% class=&amp;#34;western&amp;#34; %)
==== Contention 5-Solvency: ====

(% class=&amp;#34;western&amp;#34; %)
==== Narrowing the definition of national security to exclude “energy assets” insulates the CFIUS process from protectionist manipulation. ====

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in; &amp;#34; %)
